## 5. Accessibility

### Required

- `aria-label` on icon-only buttons: `<Button aria-label="Close" icon={<TimesIcon />} />`
- Form inputs inside `<FormGroup label="Field name">`
- Keyboard navigation: all interactive elements reachable via Tab
- Focus visible: never hide focus outlines
- Color is not the only indicator: add text or icons alongside status colors
- Touch targets: minimum 44x44px

### PatternFly Handles

- Modal focus trap and return
- Table sort announcements
- Nav keyboard navigation
- Alert live regions

