## 6. API Client Layer

```typescript
import { apiFetch } from './client';
import type { Launch } from '@cnv-monitor/shared';

export const fetchLaunches = (params?: { version?: string }): Promise<Launch[]> =>
  apiFetch('/launches', { params });
```

- One file per resource in `api/`
- Functions wrap `apiFetch` / `apiPost` only
- Return typed promises using generics
- Don't handle errors here -- TanStack Query handles them

